typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		agaagaid as string,
		agaiyear as short,
		agaagno as integer,
		agaagname as string,
		agaoffice as integer,
		agabusndiv as integer,
		agabusnsec as integer,
		agabusncla as integer,
		agasource as long,
		agaorgins as long,
		agastdate as date,
		agaendate as date,
		agauwsign as string,
		agaausign as string,
		agaclmsign as string,
		agaisic as string,
		agaadjsign as string,
		agaeosign as string,
		agasitid as string,
		againtnote as string,
		agadatest as date,
		agauat as string,
		agaordercode as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select\nagaagaid,\n		agaiyear,\n		agaagno,\n		agaagname,\n		agaoffice,\n		agabusndiv,\n		agabusnsec,\n		agabusncla,\n		agasource,\n		agaorgins,\n		agastdate,\n		agaendate,\n		agauwsign,\n		agaausign,\n		agaclmsign,\n		agaisic,\n		agaadjsign,\n		agaeosign,\n		agasitid,\n		againtnote,\n		agadatest,\n		agauat,\n		agaordercode\nfrom dwh_stage.p_agatable',
	format: 'query') ~> agatable
source(output(
		agzagzid as string,
		agzcefoty as string,
		agzcurrgrosepi as long,
		agzepicurr as string,
		agzextadjynsw as string,
		agzfagntno as long,
		agzgtepi as long,
		agznoofobjepi as integer

	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',

	format: 'query') ~> agztable

		underwriting_year_end_date as date
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,

	query: 'select day ,  underwriting_year_number, underwriting_year_start_date,\nunderwriting_year_end_date\nfrom dwh_stage.sta_dim_time',
	format: 'query') ~> DimTime
ppebtable select(mapColumn(
		pebpeaid,
		pebpever,
		pebisolan
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> pebtableselect
ppebtable select(mapColumn(
		pebpeaid,
		pebpever
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> pebtablemax
pebtablemax aggregate(groupBy(pebpeaid),
	pebpever = max(pebpever)) ~> MaxPebver
pebtableselect, MaxPebver join(pebtableselect@pebpeaid == MaxPebver@pebpeaid
	&& pebtableselect@pebpever == MaxPebver@pebpever,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> pebisolan
agatable, agztable join(agaagaid == agzagzid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> AgaAgz
AgaAgz, pebtable join(agasource == pebpeaid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> AgaPeb
AgaPeb select(mapColumn(
		agaagaid,
		agaiyear,
		agaagno,
		agaagname,
		agaoffice,
		agabusndiv,
		agabusnsec,
		agabusncla,
		agasource,
		agaorgins,
		agastdate,
		agaendate,
		agauwsign,
		agaausign,
		agaclmsign,
		agaisic,
		agaadjsign,
		agaeosign,
		agasitid,
		againtnote,
		agadatest,
		agauat,
		agzagzid,
		agzcefoty,
		agzcurrgrosepi,
		agzepicurr,
		agzextadjynsw,
		agzfagntno,
		agzgtepi,
		agznoofobjepi,
		pebisolan,
		agaordercode
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> AgaCol
pebisolan select(mapColumn(
		pebpeaid = pebtableselect@pebpeaid,
		pebpever = pebtableselect@pebpever,
		pebisolan
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> pebtable
tcrossreference filter(source_system=='PARIS' && code_type_id==460) ~> ParisMarketArea
ParisMarketArea select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_market_area = source_code_key,
		target_code_market_area = target_code,
		target_desc_market_area = target_description
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefMarketArea
tcrossreference filter(source_system=='PARIS' && code_type_id==329) ~> ParisEmployee
ParisEmployee select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_def_clm_h = source_code_key,
		target_code_def_clm_h = target_code
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefEmpDefClmHandler
tcrossreference filter(source_system=='PARIS' && code_type_id==45) ~> ParisVesslType
ParisVesslType select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_vessel_type = source_code_key,
		target_code_vessel_type = target_code,
		target_desc_vessel_type = target_description
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefVesselType
tcrossreference filter(source_system=='PARIS' && code_type_id==806) ~> ParisMarketSegment
ParisMarketSegment select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_MarkSegemnt = source_code_key,
		target_code_MarkSegemnt = target_code,
		target_desc_MarkSegemnt = target_description,
		code2_MarkSegemnt = code2
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefMarketSegment
ParisEmployee select(mapColumn(
		source_code_defclmadj = source_code_key,
		target_code_defclmadj = target_code
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefEmpDefClmAdjuster
ParisEmployee select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_UW = source_code_key,
		target_code_UW = target_code,
		target_desc_UW = target_description
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefEmpUW
ParisEmployee select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_UwResp = source_code_key,
		target_code_UwResp = target_code,
		target_desc_UwResp = target_description
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefEmpUwResp
ParisEmployee select(mapColumn(
		source_system_uwass = source_code_key,
		target_code_uwass = target_code,
		target_desc_uwass = target_description
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefEmpUwAss
tcrossreference filter(source_system=='PARIS' && code_type_id==813) ~> ParisAgreementTypeDetail
ParisAgreementTypeDetail select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_agt_det = source_code_key,
		targe_code_agt_det = target_code,
		target_desc_agt_det = target_description
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefAgreementTypeDet
tcrossreference filter(source_system=='PARIS' && code_type_id==112) ~> ParisOffice
ParisOffice select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_office = source_code_key,
		target_desc_office = target_description
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefOffice
tcrossreference filter(source_system=='PARIS' && code_type_id==809) ~> ParisUwAssistTeam
ParisUwAssistTeam select(mapColumn(
		source_code_key_uwassteam = source_code_key,
		target_code_uwassteam = target_code,
		target_desc_uwassteam = target_description
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> XrefUwAssistTeam
AgaCol derive(broker_id = case(agabusncla==8, iifNull(agzfagntno,case(agasource==agaorgins,toLong(case(1!=1,1)), agasource)), case(agasource==agaorgins, toLong(case(1!=1,1)), agasource)),
		agaoffice_string = toString(agaoffice,'##########0')) ~> AgaBroker
SrcSfCompany select(mapColumn(
		sf_company_id_broker = company_id,
		sf_company_name_broker = company_name,
		sf_source_system_id_broker = source_system_id
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SfCompanyBroker
SrcSfCompany select(mapColumn(
		sf_client_lost_reason = client_lost_reason,
		sf_company_id_client = company_id,
		sf_company_name_client = company_name,
		sf_company_owner_full_name = company_owner_full_name,
		sf_source_system = source_system,
		sf_source_system_id = source_system_id,
		sf_market_area_code = gard_market_area_code,
		sf_market_area_desc = gard_market_area_desc
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SfCompanyClient
AgaBroker, XrefOffice join(toString(agaoffice,'########0') == source_code_key_office,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinOffice
JoinOffice, XrefAgreementTypeDet join(toString(agabusncla,'#########0') == source_code_key_agt_det,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinAgreementTypeDet
JoinAgreementTypeDet, XrefUwAssistTeam join(agauat == source_code_key_uwassteam,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinUwAssistTeam
JoinUwAssistTeam, XrefEmpUwAss join(agaausign == source_system_uwass,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinUwAssist
JoinUwAssist, XrefEmpUW join(agauwsign == source_code_key_UW,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinUw
JoinUw, XrefEmpUwResp join(agaeosign == source_code_key_UwResp,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinUwResp
JoinUwResp, XrefEmpDefClmAdjuster join(agaadjsign == source_code_defclmadj,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinDefClmAdj
JoinUwYear, SfCompanyClient join(agaorgins == sf_source_system_id,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinSfClient
JoinSfClient, SfCompanyBroker join(agasource == sf_source_system_id_broker,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinSfBroker
JoinDefClmHandl, XrefMarketArea join(agasitid == source_code_key_market_area,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinMarketArea
JoinMarketArea, XrefMarketSegment join(pebisolan == source_code_key_MarkSegemnt,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinMarketSegment
JoinMarketSegment, XrefVesselType join(agzcefoty == source_code_key_vessel_type,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinVesselType
DimTime select(mapColumn(
		day,
		underwriting_year_number,
		underwriting_year_start_date,
		underwriting_year_end_date
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> UwYear
JoinVesselType, UwYear join(agastdate == day,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinUwYear
AgtUwYrMarket derive(agreement_reference = concat(toString(agaiyear,'0000'), Agreement_type , lpad(toString(agaagno,'#####0'),6,'0')),
		na_desc = 'Not Applicable',
		na_id = 1,
		na_code = 'N') ~> AgreementRef
JoinSfBroker derive(Agreement_type = case(agabusndiv==1, 'M', case(agabusndiv==2, 'E', case(agabusndiv==3, 'B', 'P'))),
		agr_uw_year = case(agabusnsec==91, toString(agaiyear,'0000'), toString(underwriting_year_number,'0000')),
		agr_uw_year_numeric = case(agabusnsec==91, agaiyear, toShort(underwriting_year_number)),
		agr_uw_year_days = (underwriting_year_end_date - underwriting_year_start_date) ,
		agr_market_segment_code = case(target_code_market_area=='OWN', 'OWN', 
case( in(['N/A','NA'],iifNull(target_code_market_area,'N/A')), 'NA', 'SPEC')),
		agr_market_segment = case(target_code_market_area=='OWN', 'Shipowners', 
case( in(['N/A','NA'],iifNull(target_code_market_area,'N/A')), 'Not Assigned', 'Specialty')),
		agr_market_segment_split_code = target_code_market_area,
		agr_market_segment_split = target_desc_market_area,
		agr_market_area_code = case(target_code_market_area == 'OWN', target_code_MarkSegemnt, target_code_market_area),
		agr_market_area = case(target_code_market_area == 'OWN', target_desc_MarkSegemnt, target_desc_market_area),
		agr_market_area_sort = case(target_code_market_area == 'OWN', code2_MarkSegemnt, 
concat('Z',target_desc_market_area)),
		agr_sf_key = concat(sf_source_system,toString(sf_source_system_id))) ~> AgtUwYrMarket
JoinDefClmAdj, XrefEmpDefClmHandler join(agaclmsign == source_code_key_def_clm_h,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinDefClmHandl
AgreementRef select(mapColumn(
		pk_key = agaagaid,
		agr_date_start = agastdate,
		agr_date_end = agaendate,
		agr_uw_year,
		agr_reference = agreement_reference,
		agr_office = target_desc_office,
		agr_uw_code = target_code_UW,
		agr_uw_description = target_desc_UW,
		agr_agreement_name = agaagname,
		agr_market_area_code,
		agr_market_area_desc = agr_market_area,
		agr_member_number = agaorgins,
		agr_sf_market_area_code = sf_market_area_code,
		agr_sf_market_area_desc = sf_market_area_desc,
		agr_sf_company_id = sf_company_id_client,
		agr_sf_key,
		agr_sf_client_lost_reason = sf_client_lost_reason,
		agr_sf_company_name_client = sf_company_name_client,
		agr_sf_company_owner = sf_company_owner_full_name,
		agr_sf_company_name_broker = sf_company_name_broker,
		agr_sf_top_group_client = na_desc,
		agr_sf_top_group_client_id = na_id,
		agr_sf_company_broker_id = sf_company_id_broker,
		agr_sf_top_group_broker = na_desc,
		agr_sf_top_group_broker_id = na_id,
		agr_def_clhndl_dry_cargo_pri = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhndl_pi_crew_pri = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhandl_casualty_pri = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhandl_defence_pri = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhandl_liquid_ca_pri = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhandl_environm_pri = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhndl_dry_cargo_sec = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhndl_pi_crew_sec = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhandl_casualty_sec = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhandl_defence_sec = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhandl_liquid_ca_sec = na_desc,
		agr_def_clhandl_environm_sec = na_desc,
		agr_dev_claims_handler_paris = target_code_def_clm_h,
		agr_uw_assist_code = target_code_uwass,
		agr_uw_assist_description = target_desc_uwass,
		agr_club_retention = na_id,
		charterers_trad_clm_team_ind = na_code,
		agr_def_claim_adjuster = target_code_defclmadj,
		agr_dummy_ind = na_code,
		agr_club_retention_stat = na_id,
		agr_abatement_usd = na_id,
		agr_abatement_stat = na_id,
		agr_uw_year_days,
		agr_resp_uw_code = target_code_UwResp,
		agr_resp_uw_desc = target_desc_UwResp,
		agr_ext_adjuster_ind = agzextadjynsw,
		agr_order_code = agaordercode,
		agr_internal_note = againtnote,
		agr_date_established = agadatest,
		agr_market_segm_cnt_grp_code = target_code_MarkSegemnt,
		agr_market_segm_country_group = target_desc_MarkSegemnt,
		agr_market_segm_cnt_grp_sort = code2_MarkSegemnt,
		agr_market_segment_code,
		agr_market_segment,
		agr_market_segment_split_code,
		agr_market_segment_split,
		agr_market_area_sort,
		agr_uw_assist_team_code = target_code_uwassteam,
		agr_uw_assist_team_desc = target_desc_uwassteam,
		agr_agreement_type_detail_code = targe_code_agt_det,
		agr_agreement_type_detail_desc = target_desc_agt_det,
		agr_est_total_gross_ton = agzgtepi,
		agr_main_vessel_type_code = target_code_vessel_type,
		agr_main_vessel_type_desc = target_desc_vessel_type,
		agr_est_premium_currency_code = agzepicurr,
		agr_est_premium_org = agzcurrgrosepi
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select1
Select1 alterRow(upsertIf(true())) ~> AlterRow1
AlterRow1 sink(input(
		pk_key as string,
		agr_sf_client_lost_reason as string,
		agr_sf_company_name_broker as string,
		agr_def_clhandl_casualty_pri as string,
		agr_sf_company_owner as string,
		agr_uw_description as string,
		agr_dummy_ind as string,
		agr_market_area_desc as string,
		agr_agreement_type_detail_code as string,
		agr_abatement_usd as decimal(28,10),
		gic_cover_request_id as decimal(28,10),
		agr_sf_company_name_client as string,
		gic_small_craft_ind as decimal(28,10),
		agr_date_end as date,
		agr_agreement_type_detail_desc as string,
		agr_main_vessel_type_code as string,
		agr_def_clhandl_defence_pri as string,
		agr_def_clhandl_defence_sec as string,
		agr_main_vessel_type_desc as string,
		agr_uw_assist_team_desc as string,
		agr_market_area_short_desc as string,
		agr_partner_team_grp_name as string,
		agr_date_established as date,
		agr_def_clhandl_environm_sec as string,
		agr_business_area as string,
		agr_sf_market_area_desc as string,
		agr_uw_year as string,
		agr_order_code as string,
		inserted_by as string,
		agr_sf_top_group_broker_id as decimal(28,10),
		agr_team_resp_uw_desc as string,
		agr_sf_company_id as decimal(28,10),
		agr_est_premium_org as decimal(28,10),
		agr_def_clhndl_pi_crew_pri as string,
		agr_agreement_type as string,
		last_updated_by as string,
		agr_uw_code as string,
